ygData.messageBody:
Noticed that the higher lvl guys always visit highpass nowadays. May I
know where is it? What monsters (lvl?), loots can be found there? Thx.

Until now, I still dun get it why armor like woven cost so much higher than
clothes if woven is just 1 AC more than clothe items? No doubt they r
magical, but does the 'magical' feature give extra protection other than
the 1 AC more?

I'm now looking for a nice pair of earrings, preferably something that can
boost my INT or AGI by at least 2. Any advice? Pricing?

Zil
